Brain Ready! project by Xenia Serbin

If you have troubles concentrating, play the Colors or Shape game for a minute and try to answer as many questions correctly as you can. After that return to your activity and notice improvement in concentration and productivity!
In Shapes game you have to decide whether the current shape matches the one shown previously.

In Colors game you have to decide whether the meaning of the word to the left matches the color of the word to the right.